What is the output of the following C code?
```c
int x = 10, y = 5;
int z = x + y * 2;
printf("%d", z);
```

What will be the output of the following code?
```c
int a = 5;
if (a == 5)
{
    printf("Equal");
}
else
{
    printf("Not equal");
}
```

What is the output of the following code?
```c
int a = 10, b = 5, c = 15;
int d = a > b ? (b > c ? b : c) : a;
printf("%d", d);
```

What is the result of the following code?
```c
int arr[5] = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
printf("%d", arr[2]);
```

What will be the output of the following code?
```c
char str[] = "Hello, World!";
